comment: Smart (BOS) sets the screen on Curry (DAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Matthews (DAL) allows Thomas (BOS) to land following the jump shot attempt.
Thomas (BOS) makes marginal contact with Barnes (DAL) that does not affect his movement to the basket.
Anderson (DAL) keeps the ball in play by striking it with a fist.
Barnes (DAL) makes contact with Thomas (BOS) that affects his SQBR.
Thomas (BOS) reaches in but does not make any contact with Barnes (DAL) that affects his SQBR to the basket.
[Observable in enhanced video] Smart (BOS) moves his pivot foot. The official is looking for any illegal contact and does not pick up the pivot foot.
Barnes (DAL) makes contact with Thomas (BOS) that affects his SQBR.
Bradley (BOS) makes marginal contact with Curry (DAL) that does not affect his SQBR.
